OL,4,CCats must be microchipped under animal
OL,5,Ccare plan
OL,6, Microchipping pet cats will become
OL,7, compulsory under a wide-ranging new
OL,8, animal welfare plan.
OL,10,FEnvironment Secretary George Eustice
OL,11,Ftold the BBC the policy would be
OL,12,Fmonitored by vets and enforced in the
OL,13,Fsame way as it is for dogs, which he
OL,14,Fsaid has led to over 90% compliance.
OL,16,FThe plan will also formally recognise
OL,17,Fthe sentience of many animals.
OL,19,FBut Mr Eustice said this measure was
OL,20,Faimed at pets and livestock, rather
OL,21,Fthan wild animals.
